data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom family townhome in the highly sought-after Peppermill subdivision!  Features include a 2 car garage, spacious kitchen with diner-style booth seating, first-floor washer and dryer connections, a stonewall wood-burning fireplace in the dining room-family room combo, and a backyard overlooking a serene lake, offering gorgeous sunsets. Enjoy the convenience of nearby shopping and a quick 15-minute drive to the St. Johns Town Center. Plus, with a new roof and AC in 2023, this home is ready for your personal touch. Make it your own and create lasting memories in this peaceful cul-de-sac retreat!  All information pertaining to the property is deemed reliable, but not guaranteed. Information to be verified by the Buyer.
